<x-legal-page title="Cookie Policy" updated="May 27, 2026" :sections="[

    'Overview' => 'This Cookie Policy explains how BotHost Pro uses cookies and similar technologies when you visit or use our platform. Cookies help us keep you signed in, remember your preferences, and understand how the platform is used. By continuing to use BotHost Pro, you consent to the use of cookies as described in this policy.',

    'What Cookies Are' => 'Cookies are small text files that a website or web application stores on your browser or device when you visit. They allow the site to recognize your browser on future visits and remember information such as your session, language preference, or interface settings. Cookies are not programs and cannot execute code or carry viruses.',

    'Cookies We Use' => [
        'Session cookies that are temporary and expire when you close your browser.',
