    'Authentication Cookies' => 'Authentication cookies are essential to the platform. They verify your login session and keep you securely signed in as you navigate the dashboard and manage your bots. Without these cookies, you would need to sign in on every page. These cookies are tied to your account session and expire when you sign out or after an inactivity period.',

    'Preference Cookies' => 'Preference cookies remember choices you make on the platform, such as interface settings, workspace configurations, or other user-selected options. These cookies improve your experience by restoring your preferred settings when you return to the platform.',

    'Security Cookies' => 'Security cookies help protect the platform from abuse, fraud, and cross-site request forgery attacks. They may store CSRF tokens and session identifiers that verify the authenticity of your requests. Disabling these cookies may prevent core platform features from working correctly.',

    'Analytics Cookies' => 'We may use analytics tools to understand how users interact with the platform, which features are used most, and where improvements can be made. Analytics data is used in aggregate form to improve the product and is not linked to individual identifiable users. Analytics integrations may be added or changed as the platform develops.',

    'Managing Cookies' => [
        'You can manage, block, or delete cookies through your browser settings.',
        'Most modern browsers allow you to view and control which cookies are stored.',
        'Blocking essential cookies may prevent you from signing in or using core platform features.',
